'''曲柔麗藻'''（學名：{{lang|la|''Nitella flexilis''}}）<ref name="TaiBIF">{{TaiBIF |id=121623 |binomial=Nitella flexilis |authority=Agardh |zh=曲柔麗藻 |access-date=2020-10-16 }}</ref><ref name="TaiBNET">{{TaiBNET|id=121623 |binomial=Nitella flexilis |authority=Agardh |zh=曲柔麗藻 |access-date=2020-10-16 }}</ref>，亦作'''柔曲麗藻'''<ref>{{cite book |url={{Google books |id=OXpTTxYInFwC |pg=PA335 |plain-url=yes }} |chapter=第9章 泡沫芯体夾層鑲板的設計 |title=多孔固体结构与性能 |publisher=[[清华大学出版社|清华大学出版社]] |page=335 |language=zh-hans }}</ref>，是一種棲息於淡水環境<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.algaebase.org/search/species/detail/?species_id=27202 |title=Nitella flexilis (Linnaeus) C. Agardh |access-date=2010-01-11 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017060103/https://www.algaebase.org/search/species/detail/?species_id=27202 |dead-url=no }}</ref>的{{tsl|en|Nitella|麗藻屬}}[[輪藻目|輪藻]]<ref name=BSBI07>{{cite web |title=BSBI List 2007 |publisher=Botanical Society of Britain and Ireland |url=http://www.bsbi.org.uk/BSBIList2007.xls |format=xls |dead-url=yes  |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6VqJ46atN?url=http://www.bsbi.org.uk/BSBIList2007.xls |archive-date=2015-01-25 |access-date=2014-10-17 |language=en }}</ref>。由於曲柔麗藻在[[藻類|藻類]]物種當中有着相對非常巨大的[[细胞|细胞]]大小及相對容易的{{tsl|en|Algaculture|藻類培養|培養}}，本物種常被用作藻類的[[模式生物|模式生物]]。

==形態特徵==
作為一種容易生長的大型物種，本物種可長至通常軸長30-50cm<ref name="Makino">牧野(1989)p.1199</ref>，甚或至1公尺<ref name = "tochigi">{{cite web |url=http://www.pref.tochigi.lg.jp/shizen/sonota/rdb/detail/07/0001.html |title=レッドデータブックとちぎ ヒメフラスコモ |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207012256/http://www.pref.tochigi.lg.jp/shizen/sonota/rdb/detail/07/0001.html |archive-date=2018-02-07 |access-date=2020-10-16 |language=ja }}</ref><ref name="Guiry">{{cite book |editor1=Guiry, M.D. |editor2=John, D.M. |editor3=Rindi, F. |editor4=McCarthy, T.K. |year=2007 |title=New Survey of Clare Island |volume=Volume 6: The Freshwater and Terrestrial Algae |publisher={{tsl|en|Royal Irish Academy|皇家愛爾蘭學院|Royal Irish Academy}} |isbn=978-1-904890-31-7 |language=en }}</ref>。

==分佈==
本物種見於除[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]以外的世界各大洲<ref name=IUCN>{{cite journal |title=''Nitella flexilis'' (Stonewort) |publisher=IUCN |doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.2011-1.RLTS.T177256A7400738.en|year = 2010}}</ref>，但以北半球為主<ref name="Makino"/>。在歐洲的[[爱尔兰岛|爱尔兰岛]]，有多個郡皆見其踪影，從[[戈尔韦|戈尔韦]]的[[Eglinton_Canal|Eglinton Canal]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Pybus | first1 = C. | last2 = O'Halloran | first2 = P. | year = 2009 | title = Distribution of some submerged aquatic macrophytes in the Eglinton Canal, Galway | url = | journal = Ir. Nat. J. | volume = 30 | issue = | pages = 51–53 }}</ref>到[[唐郡|唐郡]]和[[倫敦德里郡|倫敦德里郡]]<ref>Morton, O. ''in'' Hackney, P. 1992. ''The Flora of the North-east of Ireland''. Institute of Irish Studies and The Queen's University Belfast. {{ISBN|0-85389-446-9}}</ref>、以及Clare Island的River Dorree<ref>Co. Mayo 2004</ref><ref name="Guiry" />。

